{"tid":872632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港大叔以色列搵初戀：真係好靚","createTime":"2018-10-23T00:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:18:16.000Z","uid":8543,"like":206,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8df0ac84768e60939e361d52b4f690ab2d8e60","tid":872632,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:57:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5qPne-5NsAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5qPne-5NsAM&d=HDdcVWKqnhaKed%2FWU9HMkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=705c8193\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5qPne-5NsAM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/248526/%E5%AB%81%E5%88%B0%E9%80%99%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%82%8A%E7%AB%AF2-%E7%B5%95%E5%AF%86%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E6%90%B5%E5%88%9D%E6%88%80-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E9%9D%9A?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=yt&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F248526%2F%25E5%25AB%2581%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%2580%2599%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%25AB%25AF2-%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258F%2594%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E6%2590%25B5%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%2588%2580-%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%259D%259A%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dyt%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=HDdcVWKqnhaKed%2FWU9HMkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=350d32f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/248526/%E5%AB%81%E5%88%B0%E9%80%99%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%82%8A%E7%AB%AF2-%E7%B5%95%E5%AF%86%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%94%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E6%90%B5%E5%88%9D%E6%88%80-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E9%9D%9A?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=yt&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然以色列男人優點多多，但其實港男一點也不輸蝕。《嫁到這世界邊端2》攝製隊在當地採訪期間，就發現有三位香港大叔為了另一半，搬到以色列生活，實行「娶到這世界邊端」！<br />\n<br />\n編導黃俊輝透露，攝製隊在以色列一間中餐廳遇到他們，分別是Tony哥、雞叔和Ming哥。問到以色列女人的吸引之處，Ming哥表示：「有一度好，就係唔洗聘金、唔要彩禮，更加唔要車唔要樓，呢樣嘢已經喺中國搵唔到。」他們更稱以色列女人很美，笑言：「無論係黑過炭甚至白過雪都有！」Tony哥透露當地人觀念很開放，<span style=\"color: red;\">無論你是哪個國家的人、做什麼職業，大家都很包容。而以色列女人更不會要求男人一定要有樓先嫁，總之感覺對就會在一起。<br />\n</span><br />\n當中Ming哥就稱自己在港36年，都未曾一嚐戀愛滋味，但來到以色列就十分受歡迎。他笑稱：「因為我夠吸引力，佢搵我。（香港男人好搶手？）都係唔係，緣份。（老婆係你初戀？）係呀！」而Tony哥就稱自己最喜愛以色列的生活：「生活冇咁急促，空氣清新而且住獨立屋又大。」他們更強調在以色列生活一點也不危險，很喜歡這個國家。"},{"pid":"1b99cfb36ab4ee1a99e2e83822c115777495b588","tid":872632,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc6bc960a1e0d87559fe9d6ee404b0202cfa0d1","tid":872632,"uid":73613,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43c50b9a412c21a6719b556288193aa607391a68","tid":872632,"uid":117200,"like":198,"dislike":3,"score":195,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾01＋cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632529dbb12f3be04c46aa789c509ac4c59687e0","tid":872632,"uid":58089,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"好撚憎hk01"},{"pid":"5adf5f867b5e28624715f3d32c4bb0914a2edcf8","tid":872632,"uid":8543,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70ea16c68e9ae2a4099cfaedb06f599dfbb11f0","tid":872632,"uid":52595,"like":57,"dislike":8,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25c27efe0db7c435fe4b5bdd6fa5d89cfa736bc5","tid":872632,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"又吹奏，呢個位出左名火藥庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl